title: Brian Shaffer // 44
description:
In 2006, a 27-year-old Medical School student went out to a bar with some friends. But when they couldn't find him by last-call, they left without him. Days passed and his dad decided to file a missing persons report. But when police finally checked the bar's surveillance footage, they noticed that he was never caught leaving the bar that night. This is the disappearance of Brian Shaffer. Advertising Inquiries: https://redcircle.com/brands Privacy & Opt-Out: https://redcircle.com/privacy
